# CC PROMPT — v2.23.1 — Entity cross-reference: resolve_entity tool + infra registry

## What this does
Adds cross-system entity resolution so the agent can answer "what is kafka broker status
on worker 2?" by resolving the ambiguous name to all known identities (connection label,
IP, hostname, Proxmox VM name, Swarm node, Kafka broker).
Three changes: (1) extend infra_inventory.py with a `resolve_entity` multi-source search
and cross-reference write functions; (2) wire the Proxmox collector to populate the
inventory with VM names, vmids, IPs and node mappings; (3) add a `resolve_entity` MCP
tool to vm.py with agent allowlist registration.
Version bump: 2.23.0 → 2.23.1

